        given-names: "Przemysław"
      - name: "et al."
    year: "2021"
    url: "https://pbiecek.github.io/xai_stories/story-compas.html"
    notes: "The COMPAS explainability audit whose explainer recipe (permutation importance, partial dependence, ALE, ceteris paribus, SHAP) morie.fairness.xai independently reimplements."
